channel.title: Help with a no-ip
channel.description:
I just started a no-ip thing, I did miss silabsofts tut on a no-ip thing and so far it isn't working.
I downloaded the program, I made a no-ip thing it's called mixscape.no-ip.info
When I type ipconfig in CMD it shows this IP: 192.168.0.101
When I go to whatismyip.com it shows this: Your IP Is 206.75.103.247
I have has 2 people try all of those and they still can't connect... Here's a screenie of my no-ip program thing...
[img]http://img362.imageshack.us/my.php?image=noipyl5.png[/img] http://img362.imageshack.us/my.php?image=noipyl5.png
EDIT: I am running wireless...
